Privacy Policy

This website collects no data itself. If you click on one of the Buy buttons on the Buy page, you will be taken to a PayPal website to complete your purchase. If you do complete a purchase, Paypal will provide John Woodward's Software with your PayPal name, email address, and amount paid. This information is used ONLY to provide you with a registration code. Your information is not provided to any other third parties.
